{"tid":1069451,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"費Sir咬過的香口膠被賣天價！","createTime":"2019-03-20T03:49:32.000Z","updateTime":"2019-03-20T04:06:30.000Z","uid":173952,"like":1,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":11,"replies":[{"pid":"70f93bae107cece603d6d0cdda396c9c6fe82ab8","tid":1069451,"uid":173952,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-20T03:49:32.000Z","msg":"費格遜最後一戰的香口膠被賣掉<br />\n<br />\n  據外媒報導，費sir在執教生涯最後一戰中所嚼的香口膠，以39萬英鎊的價格賣掉了。<br />\n<br />\n  那是在2013年5月19日，曼聯已經提前獲得了那個賽季的英超冠軍，在費sir執教生涯最後一戰中，曼聯作客和西布朗戰成了5-5平。當天有一位球迷恰巧得到了費格遜在這場比賽中嚼過的香口膠。<br />\n<br />\n  近日，這名球迷將這個香口膠以39萬英鎊的價格售出，並將拍賣得到的錢款捐給了曼聯慈善基金會。這名球迷在拍賣時收到了來自各個地方的報價，凸顯了費格遜在球迷中間的影響力。<br />\n<br />\n  （來自 頭條號 直播吧）"},{"pid":"75a28a30cbced3d0ff6e390f7ff55ee379c466a6","tid":1069451,"uid":199081,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-20T03:50:24.000Z","msg":"知好有紀念價值但又好似怪怪地<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/silly.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/silly.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4c39c9d549ecf7e0a086ff02179d1078afda6d4a","tid":1069451,"uid":167330,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-20T03:52:17.000Z","msg":"想知個球迷點拾走舊香口膠<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />就咁用手？"},{"pid":"9c0acc8ff98960c09542f40d3e4824d7ecdc1a86","tid":1069451,"uid":173952,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-20T03:53:57.000Z","msg":"費sir條底褲要幾錢?"},{"pid":"115da99d7c3ab9dfac13a51598c81a02e516bf11","tid":1069451,"uid":59575,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"4c39c9d549ecf7e0a086ff02179d1078afda6d4a","tid":1069451,"uid":167330,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-20T03:52:17.000Z","msg":"想知個球迷點拾走舊香口膠<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />就咁用手？"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-20T03:55:59.000Z","msg":"放番入口"},{"pid":"5b6a6ac5d8622d2b058c90b305278730fe71ef60","tid":1069451,"uid":82720,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-20T03:57:26